## Structure

Typical monorepo structure:
```
monorepo-v2/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/        # Expo web app
│   ├── mobile/     # Expo native app
│   └── desktop/    # Electron wrapper
├── packages/
│   ├── core/       # Shared business logic
│   ├── ui/         # Shared components
│   └── ...
└── package.json
```

